fields.name: Aspire Athos
fields.description: The Aspire Athos Tank - the latest release from Aspire. The design of the Athos takes inspiration from the Aspire EXO Tank but with some added improvements to the overall functionality of the tank. The Athos tank features adjustable airflow and a brand new penta-coil head design, that holds five coils in one atomiser head with 0.16ohm resistance.

fields.name: Aspire Guroo
fields.description: The Aspire Guroo sub-ohm tank is designed for use with the Vrod 200W Vape Kit. The tank has a 2ml e-liquid capacity, leaving you plenty of room to squeeze in your favourite e-liquid. The Guroo tank features adjustable airflow, adding another layer of customisation.

fields.name: Freemax Mesh Pro
fields.description: The world's first double and triple mesh coil sub-ohm tank, FreeMax's Mesh Pro features an exquisite design and packs an almighty punch considering its minuscule size. Featuring a 2ml capacity and a thoroughly appealing design, the FreeMax Mesh Pro tank also utilises top filling and bottom airflow that has been designed for a smoother flavour.

fields.name: Smok TFV Mini V2
fields.description: The TFV Mini V2 from Smok offers a sub-ohm vaping tank that provides an immensely enjoyable vaping experience. Utilising the impressive Mini V2 A1 0.17ohm and Mini V2 A2 0.2ohm coils, this wonderful tank produces thick clouds of flavoursome vapour when paired with your preferred vape juice.

fields.name: Smok TFV18 Mini
fields.description: Introducing the brand new TFV18 Mini vape tank by Smok which provides sub-ohm vapers with the ideal tank that is small in size but big in power output. The TFV18 Mini utilises two variations of low resistance mesh coils this new Smok vape tank will create delicious flavour and vapour and can be used up to 140W.

fields.name: Uwell Crown 5
fields.description: The Uwell Crown 5 Tank is an outstanding upgrade on its predecessor, providing an excellent vaping experience for sub-ohm fans. Made from stainless steel and pyrex glass, the tank has been expertly polished to provide a sleek and smooth feel.

fields.name: Vapefly Kriemhild 2
fields.description: The Vapefly Kriemhild 2 is the new and improved version of the ever-popular Kriemhild Stock Coil sub-ohm tank. Designed with sub-ohm vapers in mind, this brilliant tank has a range of features that provide you with an unmatched vaping experience.

fields.name: Voopoo Maat
fields.description: The all new MAAT tank is compatible with the Argus GT 2 Vape Kit by VooPoo. This tank is packed with an array of new, advanced features to enhance your vaping experience. This tank uses stainless steel and Pyrex material to prevent overheating and corrosion damage.

fields.name: Voopoo PnP-X Pod Tank
fields.description: The VooPoo PnP-X Pod Tank is a vape tank that has been designed to create incredible flavour and vapour with the Drag S PnP-X and Drag X PnP-X Vape Kits. The tanks are compatible with the PnP range of coils, also manufactured by VooPoo.

fields.name: Voopoo Tpp-X Tank
fields.description: The brand new TPP X Pod tanks from VooPoo take vaping to the next level. Featuring a highly impressive 360 degree adjustable airflow, replacement mesh coils and a high power capability, the TPP X Pod Tank will offer amazing flavour and vapour production. This sub-ohm pod tank is designed for use with high VG E-Liquid and will offer a truly memorable vaping experience.

fields.name: GeekVape Zeus RDA
fields.description: The Zeus RDA by Geekvape is a brand new rebuildable dripping atomizer (RDA) that features a new aesthetically pleasing design and offers unrivalled flavour from the Z series line of vaping products. It is optimised for sub-ohm vaping and has a wide bottom airflow that creates an improved vapour production and can be easily topped up with e-liquid from the top of the atomizer and features a deep juice well that holds excess e-liquid.

fields.name: HellVape Dead Rabbit 3
fields.description: The Hellvape Dead Rabbit 3 RTA features a 2ml e-liquid capacity which can easily be filled at the top to minimise leakage. There is also a 810 drip tip as well as an adjustable airflow for a smoother performance.

fields.name: Kylin M Pro
fields.description: Check out the new Kylin M Pro RTA by Vandy Vape,improved version of the Original Kylin M. The Kylin M Pro RTA has a huge 8ml Juice Capacity while still small and compact. It measures 33.35mm (H) * 24.22mm (D). This is a Top Fill Atomizer with Top Airflow making this Leaf Proof. use the M Class Coils.

fields.name: Kylin Mesh M
fields.description: Vandyvape Kylin M RTA adopts durable and replaceable mesh coil that extend the coil life effectively. It got a top airflow intake preventing from dirty and oil leakage. The honercomb intake airhole plus trapezoidal airflow intake really enrich and blow out great massive cloud and mild flavor. What’s more, the ceramic sharpnel design built in the deck spurring the suppression in terms of different kinds of cotton volume, which also lower the rate of burning. With the top refilling device and inner juice diversion channel, comfortable and portable feeling are available.

fields.name: Wotofo Profile
fields.description: Presenting the brilliant new addition to the Wotofo team, the Profile RDTA! This RDTA is the brother of the Profile RDA and is just as brilliant

fields.name: Aspire Avp Cube Pod
fields.description: Presenting the brand-new and innovative Aspire AVP Cube Pod Kit. Ergonomically designed, the AVP Cube Kit's all-new cube shape fits perfectly in the palm of your hand, providing ultimate comfort.

fields.name: Aspire BP80
fields.description: Lightweight, compact, and capable of performing at an astonishing level, the new Aspire BP80 pod device is perfect for all levels of vapers. The Aspire BP80 pod vape kit is a state of the art e-cigarette that accommodates both new and experienced vapers.

fields.name: Voopoo Argus Pro
fields.description: Featuring style, comfort and high-level performance, the Argus Pro Pod Kit is the brand new kit from the esteemed brand VooPoo.

fields.name: Voopoo Drag-S
fields.description: The Drag S is the new, innovative pod vape kit from the esteemed Voopoo. The VooPoo Drag S kit's ergonomic design, perfectly matches the curvature of your hands, giving you ultimate comfort while you vape.

fields.name: Voopoo Drag-X
fields.description: The VOOPOO DRAG X Mod Pod Kit is full of a range of fantastic features and innovative settings, that will revolutionise your vaping experience. With a maximum output of 80W, this device packs a real punch. The Drag X is capable of producing impressive clouds whilst not compromising on flavour and utilises the delightful VooPoo PnP coils within the VooPoo PnP Pod Tank.
